The paper discusses the explainability of deep learning models, specifically capsule networks, which are a recent development in the field of machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also mentions the use of natural language processing (NLP) techniques, which falls under the sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language). Finally, the paper discusses the potential of transforming deep learning architectures, which could fall under the sub-category cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
